rComments: She is very much a prof that cares about her students. After every assignment, she would have us fill out a sheet so that she could improve the assignment. Her instructions were clear and when going into her office hours, she explained things very well and was patient. She goes by the textbook so it is important to read. Exam was long but open book

I was pleasantly surprised at just how accessible she made the course material. A truly gifted teacher. The material was wayyyy harder than I expected and I struggled a lot, and her teaching is the reason I passed at all.
